                <ul>
                    <li>Editing posts without links is broken right now.  This is actually fixed and can be accessed through catchdujour.herokapp.com, but for some reason my DNS is not seeing the JavaScript updates...</li>
                    <li>Catchegory count on user pages reflects total catchegory count rather than user's count</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>    

        <p class="click">(Click anywhere to proceed to the site)</p>
    </main>
    <script src="js/welcome.js"></script>
